Description: Asterisk Manager Interface monitor daemon for MonAst
 MonAst is a web-based real-time monitor for Asterisk PBX servers.
 .
 This package installs the Python/Twisted daemon (monast.py) that
 connects to one or more Asterisk Manager Interfaces, tracks calls,
 channels, queues and peers, and serves that state over HTTP to the
 monast-web front end. Uses the system Twisted and python3-starpy
 (https://github.com/vladonv/starpy) packages; python3-openssl and
 python3-service-identity are only needed if tls_enabled is turned on
 in daemon.conf.

